import React from 'react' import { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import { Formik, Field, Form, ErrorMessage } from 'formik'; import moment from 'moment'; const Attendance = () => { const [date, setDate] = useState(new Date()); useEffect(() => { const timer = setInterval(() => { setDate(new Date()); }, 1000); return () => { clearInterval(timer); }; }, []); const navigate = useNavigate(); useEffect(() => { if (!localStorage.getItem("token")) { navigate('/') } }, []) return ( <>
Attendance Page
Welcome user

Time : {date.toLocaleTimeString()}

Date : {date.moment().format('L')}
# In Out Status
1 Mark Otto @mdo
2 Jacob Thornton @fat
3 Larry Wild @twitter
) } export default Attendance
